Opened PR: [#10708 test(task): avoid pipefail in trust include assertions](https://github.com/jdx/mise/pull/10708)

Changed `e2e/tasks/test_task_include_trust` to use here-string `grep` checks, avoiding `grep -q` + `pipefail` false negatives when long backtraces are present.

Verified with:

```bash
mise run test:e2e tasks/test_task_include_trust
```

